               <msContents>
                  <summary>Sword of the Trinity, ሠይፈ፡ ሥላሴ፡; Prayer of Mary at Bartos, መጽሐፈ፡ ባርቶስ፡; Prayer of Our Lady Mary at Golgotha, ጸሎተ፡ እግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ዘሰኔ፡ ጎልጎታ፡; Book of the Disciples, መጽሐፈ፡ አርድእት፡; Prayer of Moses which saved him from Pharoah, ጸሎተ፡ ሙሴ፡; Image of the Christian Sabbath, መልክአ፡ ሰንበተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡</summary>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
